rubric.description: This is your chance to take the skills that you've learned across your Nanodegree journey and apply it to an app idea of your own. You control the vision! With your approved Stage 1 design and build plan in-hand, you will execute on your vision and build your app in Stage 2. Your project will be evaluated by a Udacity Code Reviewer according to this rubric. Be sure to review it thoroughly before you submit. All criteria must "meet specifications" in order to pass. Continue to the next node for submission and evaluation instructions.
